reviewText: We are building a mudroom and I thought this would have some good suggestions for design, flooring, organization, etc.  It was a goofy video about a woman trying to get rid of junk and keep things organized.  The whole "lauchpad" to organization idea was completely ridiculous, as they kept showing the woman and the organizer-person in space suits.  I regretted buying this and wish I could have my $15 back.  I wish I could have the 20 minutes of wasted time back too.
